Just as he was becoming unconscious the beast lifted an inquiring head and gazed at the man . 
More 'fraid of cow , '' the Harvester was muttering in a sleepy chuckle . 
Did the green one come out ? '' she asked , touching the box lightly . 
It did ! '' said the Harvester proudly , as if he were responsible for the performance . 
It is an omen ! It means that I am to have my long coveted pattern for my best candlestick . 
