There won't be the least use in your asking why' or interposing objections . 
This is my clean sweep . 
'' The Girl's smile was a little wan . 
She sank on a chair and picked up a pencil . 
Lay that down ! '' cried the Harvester . 
You haven't had permission from the Dictator to begin drawing . 
You are to sit and rest a long time . 
