You may , '' he said soberly . 
I am afraid that if you don't allow me to draw the moth at once , I'll never get it done . 
I dislike to mention it on your good day , but Aunt Molly is very restless . 
I got a neighbour's little girl to watch her and call me if I'm wanted . 
