First , you are to sit still ten minutes , shut your eyes , and rest . 
I can't sing , but I can whistle , and I'm going to entertain you so you won't feel alone . 
Ready now ! '' The Girl leaned her elbows on the table , closed her eyes , and pressed her slender white hands over them . 
Please don't call the birds , '' she said . 
